f83a578","tid":334854,"uid":125072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:46:05.000Z","msg":"想學揸筷子<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecef9efceeaeace16a482d7d39c96a69a4811ae8","tid":334854,"uid":45047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:47:04.000Z","msg":"你話揸筷子就話<br />\n我一直覺得揸筆真係寫到咪算囉<br />\n又唔係唔正宗就寫唔到字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n揸筷子都話正宗揸法會穩好多"},{"pid":"8a1b6c0cfb2f037adcba13a650f3182e56ef3b47","tid":334854,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:48:03.000Z","msg":"我以前為左寫鋼筆特登改返啱個揸筆手勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n方法係係中南買左枝staedtler ergosoft 鉛筆黎寫 (十幾蚊一枝，樣自己google)<br />\n佢個筆幹係三角柱體，拎住佢練下好輕力好輕力咁寫字，個幾禮拜就改返啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"156fd06d0260b4e6846b5cc17fab4049becd52b6","tid":334854,"uid":57367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:48:58.000Z","msg":"買枝三角圓筆"},{"pid":"9d78adf103cb07f26a16cd18ca56945cdbc26773","tid":334854,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:49:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你話揸筷子就話<br />\n我一直覺得揸筆真係寫到咪算囉<br />\n又唔係唔正宗就寫唔到字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n揸筷子都話正宗揸法會穩好多</blockquote><br />\n揸啱筆寫字唔駛咁用力<br />\n鋼筆寫字都會順啲 （因為筆頭同紙嘅角度啱，出墨順啲）"},{"pid":"9a99b2495707f3de11131a22351560c3d91e6872","tid":334854,"uid":38691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:53:31.000Z","msg":"出黎做野真係冇幾可要寫字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中學之後都已經少 寫都係寫英文睇到就得<br />\n練快d打字實際d 不過樓主想練咪練囉 冇衝突既又"},{"pid":"20db19edd026369197c18b7870b83300c9731f0d","tid":334854,"uid":126139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T17:28:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你話揸筷子就話<br />\n我一直覺得揸筆真係寫到咪算囉<br />\n又唔係唔正宗就寫唔到字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n揸筷子都話正宗揸法會穩好多</blockquote> <br />\n但通常揸錯寫得耐或者多會好攰<br />\n<br />\n利申揸筆揸筷子都係自己由錯學返啱"},{"pid":"43bc02cbb49b0b9dc51a2bb7b9e750b1a4c4d8ea","tid":334854,"uid":126139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T17:31:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該邊度開始？<br />\n自學？跟人？<br />\n矯型器？矯型筆？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小朋友筆我就見過，有冇人見過成人之類？</blockquote><br />\nfb 布衣老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始會好唔慣好慢唔識用力<br />\n寫得多就慢慢越嚟越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 過來人"},{"pid":"2e92f4ce5b7e131839e1ebbfaa5534cf5e4336f8","tid":334854,"uid":92512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T20:47:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該邊度開始？<br />\n自學？跟人？<br />\n矯型器？矯型筆？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小朋友筆我就見過，有冇人見過成人之類？</blockquote><br />\nfb 布衣老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始會好唔慣好慢唔識用力<br />\n寫得多就慢慢越嚟越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 過來人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以pm傾傾計？<br />\n想知多啲，多謝推介"},{"pid":"77893dc27c4ff655d83c0c4e18df27366149ac6b","tid":334854,"uid":92512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T20:50:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出黎做野真係冇幾可要寫字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中學之後都已經少 寫都係寫英文睇到就得<br />\n練快d打字實際d 不過樓主想練咪練囉 冇衝突既又</blockquote><br />\n同意鍵盤會取代寫字，<br />\n想搵野細藝過下癮，<br />\n唔想寫壞手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"268a45dc486d5c665c3c50a45a917113778262f9","tid":334854,"uid":92512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T20:53:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我以前為左寫鋼筆特登改返啱個揸筆手勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n方法係係中南買左枝staedtler ergosoft 鉛筆黎寫 (十幾蚊一枝，樣自己google)<br />\n佢個筆幹係三角柱體，拎住佢練下好輕力好輕力咁寫字，個幾禮拜就改返啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝幫忙。<br />\n好無知嘅問題，點解寫三角柱體筆會有幫助？<br />\n同埋有冇話要寫啲咩。。。個目標淨係好輕力寫到字？<br />\n多謝過來人嘅分享，感激不盡。"},{"pid":"8b9a99f9ba8fc9c443dd3ff079c37a0417dd5734","tid":334854,"uid":92512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T20:54:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你話揸筷子就話<br />\n我一直覺得揸筆真係寫到咪算囉<br />\n又唔係唔正宗就寫唔到字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n揸筷子都話正宗揸法會穩好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到有日寫到隻手好痛，就真係老大徒傷悲。<br />\n<br />\n當然都可能係自己嚇自己，不過有得趁後生改咪改"},{"pid":"623a8d99a0bf19222b275dce3d4f78819e83ee22","tid":334854,"uid":92512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T20:56:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想學揸筷子<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打 呢個我反而可以教你 有興趣可以pm"},{"pid":"0db048cb8bc671f7a290d0193805fd8e47ebd00a","tid":334854,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T21:30:36.000Z","msg":"好奇渣筆正確啲寫字會唔會流暢啲靚啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e36f0bd09c248ab4abe501255c4d8b09fc5243c","tid":334854,"uid":126139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:05:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該邊度開始？<br />\n自學？跟人？<br />\n矯型器？矯型筆？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小朋友筆我就見過，有冇人見過成人之類？</blockquote><br />\nfb 布衣老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始會好唔慣好慢唔識用力<br />\n寫得多就慢慢越嚟越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 過來人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以pm傾傾計？<br />\n想知多啲，多謝推介</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nok嘅 tg?"},{"pid":"d111bda543efc2be63ca57af1bceea1194cdd3b0","tid":334854,"uid":126139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:06:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好奇渣筆正確啲寫字會唔會流暢啲靚啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n靚唔靚我就覺得唔太關事<br />\n但正常係會流暢啲同